snippet.title: Universal Space Station Inc. Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Add it to your Steam wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1048550

In the midst of a global population boom and catastrophic climate change, you have been appointed captain of Universal Space Station Inc. Your mission: deliver a sustainable solution to global starvation. Our future lies in your hands.
